* She was covered in her own mech-fluid but still she knelt there, glaring 
up at Nightstrike.
< But I have to fight, I can't be finished off like this!!>
Grunting from the pain she raised herself to her feet, head tilted up at 
Nightstrike.*

" Aren't you going to come down to finish me off?!!"

* She yelled up at him, but then her eyes widened when Prowl suddenly came 
into the picture.*

" Prowl!"

* Iron growled.*

" Get out of here, this is MY fight!"
